{"tid":741054,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[Apple]手機卡左係iTunes開唔到機","createTime":"2018-07-13T10:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T11:16:51.000Z","uid":14046,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a54524e1641f24058171b8e84951f71911202f62","tid":741054,"uid":14046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"手機狀況係<br />\n開到機既<br />\n但係入唔翻開鎖畫面<br />\n一開就直接要我連iTunes<br />\niTues 要求透過用電腦接駁手機到iTunes去更新最新的IOS <br />\n手機係成功連接到iTunes既更新<br />\n但是當更新到最後 <br />\n什至可以話係行完整條進度線<br />\n但iTunes 會彈出Error（ 4013）<br />\n即係up唔到ios<br />\n我估係錯誤既Program code個類？<br />\n我拎去apple store genius bar問佢地啲員工解不到4013錯誤<br />\n話可能係手機硬件壞<br />\n剩係叫我簡洗機或者比5-7k去佢地子公司修復<br />\n請問有無巴打知仲有咩方法可以拎翻啲相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我剩係求拎得翻啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3640759d067c5d5869475369cc65561759b33c06","tid":741054,"uid":1086,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"原來係冇做backup既朋友"},{"pid":"c97c383aa917c63257d0ae439f3df23c244995ad","tid":741054,"uid":376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人類總是要犯相同錯誤"},{"pid":"02828d9b8118d4069a79286a9067e2be2bff29d6","tid":741054,"uid":53466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}